<br>
if what you want from quadding is the xp, start practicing your charming. you can effectively gain a ton more xp charming than you ever could quadding, especially in first and second tier planes.<br>
<br>
in short, Gflux is a crap spell <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :| --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/indifferent.gif ALT=":|"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
we arent wizards <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :lol --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/laugh.gif ALT=":lol"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
we arent druids <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :rollin --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/roll.gif ALT=":rollin"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
we're better than both of them combined <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START ;) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/wink.gif ALT=";)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  <p><img border=0 src="http://www.strike9.com/file.aspx/path=/Charmroxors/fullsize/barcodesig.jpg" /><br>
<a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=555166" target="_new">inspect me</a></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#deddbf><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub136.ezboard.com/beqenchantersrealm.showUserPublicProfile?gid=knotthed>Knotthed</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 3<br> <font color=#330000>(2/19/03 1:28:43 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub136.ezboard.com/feqenchantersrealmspells.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=248.topic&index=4>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Gravity Flux question</span><hr size=1> LOL.  thanks for the input.  I will definitely check out charming more as well.  I have a new charm spell at 39 too, so that might be the route to go then.  Thanks again<br>
